quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  63,9,"oh inu okhulupirira! Musalole chuma kapena ana anu kuti akusokonezeni pokukumbukira Mulungu. Ndipo aliyense amene achita motero, ndithudi, ndi wotayika"
  63,10,"Ndipo perekani kuchokera ku katundu amene takupatsani imfa isanadze pa wina wa inu kuti iye asanene kuti: “Oh Ambuye wanga! Inu mukadandibweza mwa kanthawi kochepa, ine ndikadapereka chaulere chochuluka kuchokera ku chuma changa ndikukhala mmodzi wa anthu ochita zabwino.”"
  63,11,Ndipo Mulungu sapereka nthawi kwa wina pamene nthawi yake itakwana. Ndipo Mulungu amadziwa chilichonse chimene mumachita